Package: ebrdify
Title: A handy function to make your data EBRD-friendly
Version: 0.5.0
Authors@R:
    person("Pablo", "Garcia-Guzman", email = "garciagp@ebrd.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides simple helpers to classify countries in your
    data according to the EBRD groupings, list the EBRD economies, and
    standardise country names to official EBRD / Transition Report terminology.
